verses.text: Calec wach' lolonel t'a Jehová. Ex schecab' ex Jehová, alec wach' lolonel t'ay.
Mach ex ayex ek' t'a yamaq'uil stemplo Jehová ko Diosal,
alec wach' lolonel t'ay, yujto wach'. B'itananhec t'ay yujto te ay swach'k'olal t'ayonh anima onh tik.
Ix onh sik'canel a onh israel onh yinhtilal onh winhaj Jacob, yic tzonh och yicoc.
Ha in tik wojtac wal sik'lab'il to a Jehová ko Diosal, yelxo wal ek'b'al yelk'och t'a yichanh masanil comon Dios.
Syalnhej sk'ulan masanil tas snib'ej sk'ulej, wach'chom t'a satcha’anh, ma t'a sat lu'um tik, ma t'ha ha' mar, ma pax t'a yich ha'.
A' tz'ak'ancot asun b'aj slajwik'och lum lum tik. A' tz'ak'anek' copnaj lheb'lon ayic syak'an nhab'. A' sjacanelta ik' b'aj molanek' yuj.
A' milannaccham heb' b'ab'el unin t'a junjun patil heb' aj Egipto yet' pax sb'ab'el yune' junjun nok' snok' heb'.
Ha t'a snanhal chonhab' Egipto chi', ay juntzanh tas te satub'tac sk'ulejnac yic syak'an syaelal winh rey yet' pax heb' schecab' winh.
Tzijtum juntzanh chonhab' satnaquel yuj, smilannaccham heb' rey te niwac yopisio.
Smilnaccham winhaj Sehón, sreyal heb' amorreo yet' winhaj Og sreyal Basán yet' masanil heb' rey t'a yol yic Canaán.
Axo lum sluum heb' rey chi' yak'nac t'ayonh a onh israel onh tik, yic squiquejcan lu'um.
Mamin Jehová, a a b'inajnaquil malaj b'ak'uinh ol sateloc. D'a masanil tiempo ol ach nachajcotoc.
Ha Jehová sb'oan yaj owal t'a heb' schonhab', tz'ok' sk'ol t'a heb' schecab'.
Ha sdiosal heb' ch'oc chonhab'il, nab'a oro, nab'a plata, anima sb'oani.
Ay sti' sdiosal heb' chi', palta max lolonlaj. Ay sat, palta max yil-laj.
Ay schiquin, palta max yab'laj, max yik'laj yik'.
Ha heb' sb'oan juntzanh yechel chi' yet' heb' tz'ak'anoch t'a sk'ool, lajan heb' yet'oc.
Ex wetisraelal, calec wach' lolonel t'a Jehová. Ex sacerdote, ex yinhtilal winhaj Aarón, alec wach' lolonel t'a Jehová.
Ex yinhtilal winhaj Leví, alec wach' lolonel t'a Jehová. Mach ex ay yelk'och Jehová t'a he sat, alec wach' lolonel t'ay.
Aljocab' wach' lolonel t'a Jehová t'a Sion, aton t'a Jerusalén b'aj cajan. Calec wach' lolonel t'a Jehová.
